        "text": "<p>We’re looking for a talented, hands-on <strong>Content Creator</strong> to join our small (but mighty) team. Someone with a brilliant eye, a love of interiors and a genuine obsession for beautiful craft.</p><p>If you live and breathe <strong>colour, pattern, photography, storytelling</strong>, and you can turn a simple brief into something that feels elevated and inspiring… we’d love to meet you.</p>",
