        "text_cfjFNe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "text": "<p><strong>The Role</strong></p><p>You’ll work closely with our <strong>Marketing Manager</strong>, bringing our brand to life across email, social and printed materials, helping keep our content beautifully organised and always on point.</p><p>This is a varied role where no two days look the same. One moment you might be creating a stunning mailer, the next you’re capturing behind-the-scenes content on a shoot, pulling together assets for press, or helping plan an upcoming campaign.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>Creating <strong>inspiring email campaigns / mailers</strong> with direction from our Marketing Manager</li><li>Managing and maintaining our <strong>photo library</strong> (we’ve got a lot of beautiful imagery and it needs love!)</li><li>Responding to <strong>press requests</strong> quickly and professionally with the right imagery and info</li><li>Supporting content creation for our <strong>Shopify website</strong> (you’ll need to know your way around Shopify confidently)</li><li>Making and editing <strong>Reels</strong> (and knowing what works visually + commercially)</li><li>Capturing content on shoots: <strong>video + stills</strong>, BTS, styling moments, product details</li><li>Helping create, organise and run <strong>photo shoots</strong> (planning, lists, props, structure, timing)</li><li>Producing marketing assets such as <strong>postcards, brochures, campaign graphics and digital collateral</strong></li><li>Being part of the wider brand world, keeping everything consistent, elevated and beautifully presented</li></ul>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "inset": false,
            "color_scheme": "dark_text",
            "desktop_text_box_position": "start",
            "text_align": "left"
