        "text_ttPnth": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "text": "<p><strong>You Might Be Perfect If You…</strong></p><ul><li>Have a <strong>strong aesthetic</strong> and a sharp eye for what looks premium, modern and timeless</li><li>Are <strong>obsessed with interiors</strong> and have genuine appreciation for <strong>craft and block print</strong></li><li>Know “who’s who” in the interiors/design world (and love keeping up with it)</li><li>Are organised, proactive, and calm under pressure</li><li>Are confident working independently, but love being part of a collaborative team</li><li>Can be <strong>client-facing</strong> when needed, warm, polished and professional</li><li>Are happy to stretch beyond the job description sometimes… because we’re a small team and we support each other</li></ul><p><strong>The Important Bit</strong></p><p>We’re not looking for someone who just “posts content.”<br/><br/>We’re looking for someone who can help shape and elevate how the world sees our brand, with energy, care and creativity.</p><p>If you’re excited by the idea of being part of a fast-moving, design-led business where your work genuinely makes an impact, we’d love to hear from you.</p>",
